message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and valued at $100 by you. Considering its high quality and the value it brings, I am extending this exclusive opportunity to you at an exceptional price of $95. This is a special offer designed to ensure you receive the best value while also maximizing my earnings. I believe this deal presents a fantastic opportunity for both of us. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
